PrecisTransfer to the Minister of Employment and Immigration of the powers, duties and functions of the Minister of National Health and Welfare in relation to the inspection and medical care of immigrants and in relation to the authorization or recognition of qualified medical practitioners as medical officers for the purposes of any or all provisions of the Immigration Act, effective June 1, 1993.
